Residuals requirements

Normality

full_model = lm(bwt ~., data = birthwt)
hist(full_model$residuals)

qqnorm(full_model$residuals)
qqline(full_model$residuals)

Constant Variability

plot(abs(full_model$residuals) ~ full_model$fitted.values)

Independence

plot(full_model$residuals)

I’m not sure if there is a time series structure here.

Model selection

attach(birthwt)
variables = cbind(low, age, lwt, race, smoke, ptl, ht, ui, ftv)
target = bwt
bic_searches = bicreg(variables, target, strict = F, OR = 20)
summary(bic_searches)

model_1 = train(form = bwt ~ low + race + ui, data = birthwt, method = 'lm',
                trControl = trainControl(method = 'cv', number = 10))
